Theramine is a Food and Drug Administration (FDA) regulated medical food designed to address the increased nutritional requirements associated with chronic pain syndromes and low back pain. Theramine promotes the production of the  that help manage and improve the sensory response to pain and inflammation. Theramine is available by prescription only.

Theramine is manufactured according to FDA current Good Manufacturing Practices (cGMP). All of the ingredients in Theramine are classified as generally recognized as safe (GRAS) by the FDA.

